(Try to enter the lighthouse, but there's no-one to greet you. Everyone's in the courtyard.)
<br>
---
<ol>
<li>($funcQuestUpdateLink: "You can simply indulge. Go see what the apprentices are up to.", "studentDebate", "active", "A school is where the students are. Without them, there is only dusty halls.", "This should be at least amusing.", [], "S: studentDebate 2",)

<li>(link: "Turn back. You'll return once everyone remembers that they have a school to run.")[(goto: "Apesai Lighthouse")]
</ol>

